# Auth mode (optional)
# - When set to `entra`, password-based login/registration/reset endpoints return 410 and the API expects Entra-issued access tokens.
# Set to false to reject legacy JWT_SECRET bearer tokens once Entra auth is deployed.

# Microsoft Entra ID (OIDC) for API auth
# ENTRA_TENANT_ID: your Entra tenant id (GUID)
# ENTRA_API_AUDIENCE: the API application's audience (usually the API app registration client id or Application ID URI)
# ENTRA_REQUIRED_SCOPE: delegated scope name required on access tokens (default: access_as_user)